[31/01/2019 02:39:11] <font color="#0000ff">(Ladrido)</font>
[31/01/2019 02:39:15] <font color="#0000ff">(Rugidos)</font>
[31/01/2019 02:39:18] <font color="#ffff00">Conservados</font>
[31/01/2019 02:39:18] <font color="#ffff00">en fina ceniza volcánica,</font>
